Author: MehiliUdayangani
Title: [ICO][BOUNTY] HeartBout - a social network with a decentralized incentive system
Body: Social network HeartBout was designed to convert the time spent in social networking to user earnings, where users get their profit in the form of HBC tokens for their activity as authors and voters.The design and functionality of the social network HeartBout has been developed through deep analysis of different services.

Author: goldart
Title: [ICO][BOUNTY] HeartBout - a social network with a decentralized incentive system
Body: Have you ever wondered how much time you devote to social networks? An average user spends about two hours a day on social networks, which is equivalent to five years and four months over a lifetime. Quite a significant number! How to make it so that the user would spend this time with the benefit and interest for himself, showing maximum activity, and turn the social network into an effective large-scale platform for advertisers? Author: goldart
Title: [ICO][BOUNTY] HeartBout - a social network with a decentralized incentive system
Body: With a decentralized reward system to encourage user activity, based on blockchain technology. Meet HeartBout app – a revolution in social networking communication. Social network HeartBout was designed to convert the time spent in social networking to user earnings, where users get their profit in the form of HBC tokens for their activity as authors and voters. The design and functionality of the social network HeartBout has been developed through deep analysis of different services. In HeartBout users can post photos, videos and video links from popular sources like Youtube. Within HeartBout we have developed a unique functionality - the creation of categories accumulating tags and challenges/bouts between user publications.  http://heartbout.com/

Author: goldart
Title: [ICO][BOUNTY] HeartBout - a social network with a decentralized incentive system
Body: HeartBout Bounty Campaigns is over.  Announcement https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2559327.0   WebsiteTwitterFacebookWhite PaperTelegram     HeartBout is a social network with a decentralized, blockchain-based incentive system.  Users participate in creation and promotion of content and receive rewards in the form of HBC cryptocurrency. HeartBout social network monetizes user activity in the form of publications, voting or commenting, thus supporting HBC emission by creating advertising opportunities.  HBC tokens can be spent on promotion of a publication (advertisment). It will also be possible to withdraw your coins to an accredited exchange with subsequent exchange for other currencies.  Crowd sale  Pre-ICO The number of tokens — 8 235 600 ( 10 217 279)  ICO The number of tokens — 35 962 120 ( 39 783 506) The maximum number of tokens issued for sale — 44,197,720 (  50 000 785)  Promotion to attract investors HeartBout social network launches new promotion to attract investors. Each participant can attract investors and receive a bonus of 5% of the amount from contribution. To participate in this promotion you must register on the website and in the personal Cabinet get your referral link. Everyone who registers through your link becomes your referral. After he will buy a token HBC you will automatically be credited with a bonus of 5% of its contribution.    HeartBout bounty campaign  Today HeartBout launches an official bounty campaign. We invite everyone interested to join and help us grow a large and strong community. HeartBout reserved 4% of the total number of tokens for Bitcointalk bounty program in preparation for Pre ICO. The campaign starts with the posting of this thread and will continue until 28.02.2018. Recalculation of activities and stake crediting will be performed once a week, on Sundays.  Stake distribution: 1.   Signatures Campaign: 20 % 2.   Translation and Moderation Campaign: 20 % 3.   Blog and Content bounty campaign: 25 % 4.   Facebook bounty campaign: 15 % 5.   Twitter bounty campaign: 15 % 6.   Telegram Bounty campaign: 5%   HeartBout Signatures Campaign  20% of the bounty pool is reserved for this campaign.  Rules: 1.    Only Bitcointalk users with Jr. Member rank and above are allowed to participate. 2.    Participants in the campaign are not allowed to use other signatures or avatar images until the end of the campaign. 3.    Each participant must post at least 10 messages a week. 4.    All messages must be posted in "Alternate Cryptocurrencies" or "Trading Discussion” boards. Messages on other boards will not be counted. Users may be disqualified for spam and trolling. 5.    If a participant increases his or her rank during participation in the signatures campaign, he or she must add a signature corresponding to the new rank. 6.    Use of multiple accounts is not allowed.  Stake distribution: Hero/Legendary: 2.5 stakes/week Senior Member: 2 stakes/week Full Member: 1.5 stakes/week Member: 1 stake/week Junior Member: 0.5 stakes/week  Additionally the user is granted 0.5 stakes per week for using HeartBout avatar.  Avatar:    Sign up here Check your status here  Translation & Moderation Campaign  20% of the bounty pool is reserved for this campaign Only users with Jr. Member rank and above are allowed to participate. To participate in the translation and moderation campaign, it is necessary to translate the official announcement thread and HeartBout whitepaper and post them to the local Bitcointalk board.  In addition, the participant must moderate the HeartBout thread created by him or her, answer user questions and publish the campaign news. If a participant does not moderate his or her thread, he or she will be disqualified.  Stake distribution: Announcement translation: 100 stakes White piper translation: 200 stakes Moderation: 5 stakes per message. The maximum reward that may be received by a single participant is 500 stakes.  Sign up here Check your status here   Blog and Content bounty campaign  25% of the bounty pool is reserved for this campaign.  If you can create high-quality content, such as articles, videos and other materials, you can participate in the HeartBout blog bounty campaign.  Rules: 1.    Your content must be original and unique. We do not accept copied texts and videos. 2.    All content must be publicly available. 3.    The page with the published content must include a link to HeartBout website, its pages in social networks or Bitcointalk thread. 4.    An article must be at least 200 words in length, a video must last at least 3 minutes. 5.    Any content containing negative information about HeartBout project is not allowed to participate. 6.    You are not allowed to delete or hide content until the end of the campaign.  A participant can receive from 1 to 10 stakes for the publication of content. At the same time, if a participant publishes unique content on different websites, separate reward may be granted for each publication.  The content will be evaluated by the following parameters: quality, website popularity, audience size, and also the publication date (the later the content is published, the less is the reward).  Sign up here Check your status here  Facebook bounty campaign  15% of the bounty pool is reserved for this campaign.  To participate in this campaign, subscribe to the official HeartBout Facebook page and repost the campaign publications at least 5 times a week.  In addition, the participant must post at least one of his or her own message a week, using the following hashtags: # HeartBout #ICO #Crowdsale #Bitcoin #Blockchain #Token #ETH #Ethereum #TokenSale  Rules: 1.    Only Facebook profiles with at least 300 real friends are allowed to participate. 2.    Your account must be public. 3.    Each participant can register only once, use of fake accounts is prohibited. 4.    Use of fraudulent methods to increase the number of friends, likes, reposts is prohibited. 5.    If your account is banned or suspended during the participation in HeartBout bounty campaign, you will be disqualified and lose all bounty stakes credited to you.  Sign up here Check your status here  Twitter bounty campaign  15% of the bounty pool is reserved for this campaign.  To participate in this campaign, subscribe to the official HeartBout Twitter  After the registration, it is necessary to make retweets of publications at least 5 times a week. We count only one retweet a day. If you make several retweets in the same day, they will not be counted.  In addition, the participant must post at least one of his or her own tweet a week, using the following hashtags: # HeartBout #ICO #Crowdsale #Bitcoin #Blockchain #Token #ETH #Ethereum #TokenSale  To receive a reward, each member of the Twitter bounty campaign must submit weekly reports indicating tweets and retweets. If a participant fails to submit a report, no reward will be granted.  Account requirements: 1.    Only Twitter profiles with at least 300 real subscribers are eligible to participate. 2.    Your account must be public. 3.    Each participant can register only once, use of fake accounts is prohibited. 4.    Use of fraudulent methods to increase the number of friends, likes, retweets is prohibited. 5.    If your account is banned or suspended during the participation in HeartBout bounty campaign, you will be disqualified and lose all bounty stakes credited to you.  Sign up here Check your status here Submit weekly reports here      Telegram Bounty campaign  5% of the total bounty fund will be allocated for this campaign.  Instructions:  Telegram Join link: Channel: https://t.me/heartbout Group: https://t.me/joinchat/CVZX_A7t5Fp3nJKwZFBrmg  No spam or foul language against other members or about the project. Stay till the end of the ICO to get the bounty.  Sign up here Check your status here  WebsiteTwitterFacebookWhite PaperTelegram

Author: goldart
Title: [ICO][BOUNTY] HeartBout - a social network with a decentralized incentive system
Body: Russian announcement thread: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2572103.0 indonesian thread https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2575923 Filipino Announcement: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2584131.0 Chinese thread: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2589554.0 https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2589475.0   Invite to HeartBout telegram: https://t.me/heartbout   Today social networks are an integral part of life of every person. We can’t imagine a single day without taking part in communities, exchanging messages with friends, looking for new friendships, getting new information from our news feed, which… https://t2p.pw/OsEmZo16go   The ICO website consists of lending and users' personal cabinets participating in the purchase of HBS tokens.  Landing provides general information of performed ICO. On this page you can find the information about the concept and economy of the created… https://t2p.pw/pBUt9gfqiL  With a decentralized reward system to encourage user activity, based on blockchain technology. Meet HeartBout app – a revolution in social networking communication. Social network HeartBout was designed to convert the time spent in social networking to user earnings, where users get their profit in the form of HBC tokens for their activity as authors and voters. The design and functionality of the social network HeartBout has been developed through deep analysis of different services. In HeartBout users can post photos, videos and video links from popular sources like Youtube. Within HeartBout we have developed a unique functionality - the creation of categories accumulating tags and challenges/bouts between user publications. http://heartbout.com/   The design of the HeartBout app was carefully thought out. Through analysis of a large number of products with similar functionality, we chose the best way of presenting the application interface. https://heartbout.com/   Russian cryptocurrency media Coinspot.io wrote about our project: https://coinspot.io/company/socialnaya-set-heartbout-s-sistemoj-pooshhreniya-aktivnosti-polzovatelej-provodit-pre-ico/   Bets are placed by a challenger and must be confirmed by another participant. Thus, the prize fund is formed and consists of the challenger’s and the recipient’s amount of tokens. The winner gets a prize fund minus a commission for HeartBout social network.   The Social Network of the New Generation HeartBout with a Decentralized Reward System of User’s Activity Conducts Pre-ICO http://www.newsbtc.com/2017/12/20/social-network-new-generation-heartbout-decentralized-reward-system-users-activity-conducts-pre-ico/   Have you ever wondered how much time you devote to social networks? An average user spends about two hours a day on social networks, which is equivalent to five years and four months over a lifetime. Quite a significant number! How to make it so that the user would spend this time with the benefit and interest for himself, showing maximum activity, and turn the social network into an effective large-scale platform for advertisers? The HeartBout project will answer this question: https://goo.gl/Xw9svi   This is a paid-for submitted press release.
